<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I was fortunate enough to purchase a blood fork.  I am seeing them around more and more.  Since I am a troll, I've been using 2hs exclusively.  My piercing skill is now 6.  I don't worry about keeping my skills up.  Now that I have a piercing weapon, I just get in a group and watch my skill go up fast due to the low delay.  Sure I miss alot, but if we get into serious trouble, I just switch back to the Dark Reaver.</font></td></tr></table>
